snippet.title: Sabre Team gameplay (PC Game, 1992)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Sabre Team, Dos PC game produced by Krisalis in 1992 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/sabre-team/4971/
Selecting and equipping a team to take on the bad guys in this turn-based strategy game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
